# Homelab documentation

**Create or update homelab / cluster documentation in [nerd.dad](https://github.com/nerddotdad/nerd.dad)** under `docs/homelab/`. It is published via GitHub Pages at https://nerd.dad/latest/homelab/.

| Task | Where |
|------|--------|
| Guides (cluster overview, kubectl ref, etc.) | **nerd.dad** → `docs/homelab/guides/` |
| Hand-written docs, runbooks | **nerd.dad** → `docs/homelab/` |
| Runbook snippets | **nerd.dad** → `includes/homelab/runbook/` |
| HelmRelease / PrometheusRule / Flux YAML | this repo (`clusters/`) |
| Alert `runbook_url` annotations | this repo — use `https://nerd.dad/latest/homelab/kubernetes/...` |

Keep this repo **manifests-only**: no root `*.md` guides (except a short `README.md` pointing at nerd.dad).
